[SDG-PKG]: Install a package with: sdgpkg install <name>
[SDG-PKG]: List installed packages with: sdgpkg list
[SDG-PKG]: Update all packages with: sdgpkg upgrade
[SDG-PKG]: Search available packages with: sdgpkg fetch
[SDG-PKG]: Check for updates with: sdgpkg upgradable
[SDG-PKG]: View package info with: sdgpkg info <name>
[SDG-PKG]: Remove a package with: sdgpkg uninstall <name>
[SDG-PKG]: Clone without installing with: sdgpkg sync <name>
